title: TWO BEDROOM FOR RENT IN EDGEWATER
posting_body: ['LISTING ID 6301732', "This apartment located in a rental community in Miami features living room, dining room, central A/C, front-load washer and dryer in-unit, wood plank flooring, spacious walk-in closets, 10' ceiling height, chef-style kitchens,", "42'' upper cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, floating kitchen island, bathrooms with quartz countertops, designer tile backsplash, double sink vanities, and glass showers.", 'Community offers elevator access, resort-inspired pool, private pool side cabanas, spa,', 'sundeck and outdoor bar and grill, clubroom lounge with bar, billiards table, large flat screen TVs & WiFi, office suite with private room and conference room, fitness center, Yoga & Spin studio with Peloton Bikes, and dog washing station.', 'Off-street parking and electric car charging stations.', 'Pet friendly.', 'Located within 5 minutes of The Shops at Midtown Miami, The Salty Donut, I-395 and I-195 and Starbucks.', 'LISTING ID 6301732', '*PLEASE REFERENCE ABOVE LISTING ID', 'WHEN INQUIRING*', 'Stop searching.', 'You’ve already come to the right place.', 'If you’re looking for ANY type of property whether it’s a studio, an apartment, a townhouse or single family home...', 'YES WE GOT IT.', 'We’re a ONE STOP shop that can assist you in taking the next step towards your next home today.', 'No one makes it this easy!', 'Just send us a text to', 'show contact info', 'with your name and we can send you a CUSTOM list of properties that match what you’re looking for and get the process started.', 'Thank you!', 'Hannah Edwards', '*DISCLAIMER - We do post properties for a 30 day period of time.', 'Due to High Rental Demand, some properties advertised may be withdrawn, cancelled, rented, pending or sold within the past 30 days.', 'All information is deemed to be correct, but not guaranteed*']
